%N A372091 G.f. A(x) satisfies A(x) = 1/( 1 - 9*x*A(x)*(1 + x*A(x)) )^(1/3).
%H A372091 Robert Israel, <a href="/A372091/b372091.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..762</a>
%F A372091 a(n) = (1/(n+1)) * Sum_{k=0..n} 9^k * binomial(n/3+k-2/3,k) * binomial(k,n-k).
%F A372091 a(n) = 9^n*binomial((4*n-2)/3, n)*hypergeom([(1-n)/2, -n/2], [(2-4*n)/3], -4/9)/(n+1). - _Stefano Spezia_, Apr 18 2024
